text.Prompt:
The following is a product description written by our marketing expert using the following product keywords and product title.

Product title:
ReadyPlug USB Cable Compatible with HP 1320 LaserJet Printer (10 Feet, Black)

Product keywords:
ReadyPlug Data Cable Compatible with HP 1320 LaserJet Printer
USB 2.0 High Speed Cable upto 480mbps
Length: 10 Feet (3 Meters) - Color: Black
Reduces strain on device port
Keeps cable out of the way
Protected from EMI/RFI interference
Uses an outer foil shield, inner braid shield and twisted-pair composition to ensure performance
For PC or Mac Computer

Product description:
text.Response A: This ReadyPlug USB cable is very long and black. It’s for connecting a computer to a HP 1320 LaserJet printer.
text.Response B: ReadyPlug USB Cable is compatible with HP 1320 LaserJet Printer. This cable is 10 feet long and black in color. This cable is high speed USB 2.0 cable that supports 480Mbps. It is protected from EMI/RFI interference. It uses an outer foil shield, inner braid shield and twisted-pair composition to ensure performance. It is suitable for both PC and Mac computers. It reduces strain on device port and keeps the cable out of the way.
